---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <article class="home">
    <section class="bio">
      <p>
        I am a Staff Computer Vision and Robotics Engineer at
        <a href="https://www.deltia.ai/">Deltia GmbH</a>, a venture-backed
        Berlin startup founded within the
        <a href="https://www.merantix.com/">Merantix</a> ecosystem.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build Vision-Language Models for manufacturing.
        My work enables insights through temporal action segmentation
        and uses these models in robotic learning to automate assembly tasks.
      </p>
      <p>
        I did my Ph.D. at
        <a href="https://www.visinf.tu-darmstadt.de/visual_inference/people_vi/stefan_roth.en.jsp">TU Darmstadt</a>
        under Stefan Roth in the Visual Inference Group.
        During that time I worked at Volkswagen Group Research and CARIAD SE,
        building the decision-making and planning system for automated driving.
        My research unified prediction and planning to enable humanlike,
        assertive driving in interactive environments.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am passionate about AI systems that work under real-world conditions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="recent">
      <h2>News</h2>
      <ul class="recent-list">
        <li>
          <span class="date">2024-11-01</span>
          <span>Started as a Staff Computer Vision and Robotics Engineer at Deltia GmbH.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="date">2020-10-01</span>
          <span>Transitioned from Volkswagen Group Research to CARIAD SE.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="now">
      <h2>Now</h2>
      <p class="text-dim">
        Building Vision-Language Models for manufacturing, enabling
        temporal action segmentation and leveraging these models in
        robotic learning to automate manual assembly tasks.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="newsletter">
      <h2>Newsletter</h2>
      <p class="text-dim">Occasional updates on my work and research.</p>
      <form
        action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/sascharosbach"
        method="post"
        class="newsletter-form"
      >
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        <input type="hidden" name="embed" value="1" />
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .home {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
  }

  .recent-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .recent-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5em;
    padding: 0.5em 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .recent-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .date {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    min-width: 8em;
  }

  .now p {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border-light);
    padding-left: 1em;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5em;
    margin-top: 1em;
  }

  .newsletter-form input[type="email"] {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.5em 0.75em;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: inherit;
    background: var(--bg-main);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 2px;
    color: var(--fg-main);
  }

  .newsletter-form input[type="email"]::placeholder {
    color: var(--fg-faint);
  }

  .newsletter-form button {
    padding: 0.5em 1.25em;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: inherit;
    background: var(--fg-main);
    color: var(--bg-main);
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-main);
    border-radius: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .newsletter-form button:hover {
    background: var(--fg-dim);
    border-color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
</style>
